gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter
Class InstrumentDataSet

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter.InstrumentDataSet

public class InstrumentDataSet
extends java.lang.Object

The InstrumentDataSet is what defines a PrepService. It contains instrument specific data. Currently, this class does not have big an impact since the preprocessing can be done generically by GenPrepService. The class' importance might become more apparent with increasing preprocessing complexity.
